data.description: Gorgeous all brick home in the desirable Landings subdivision in Lynn Haven. You'll love this custom built, split floor plan, with over 3,100 sq. ft. of comfortable living space for you to enjoy.  As you step inside, you'll be greeted by an abundance of natural light,  palatial columns, high ceilings, moldings and a spacious layout. The heart of the home is a beautifully appointed kitchen with stainless steel appliances, maple cabinets, breakfast bar and breakfast nook. The living room is an inviting space, featuring a cozy fireplace, built-ins, and large windows that provide scenic views of the pool and golf course. The patio and saltwater pool are fully enclosed and there is plenty of room for entertaining outside. Whether you're enjoying a quiet evening at home or entertaining family and friends, this area will be a favorite gathering spot. The primary suite features a great sized walk in closet, private access to the patio, and a full bathroom. The three additional bedrooms have plenty of room for sleep and study and have access to two additional full bathrooms. One bedroom located at the back of the home is perfect as a mother-in-law or guest suite with its own entrance and the full bath conveniently located just steps away! This home also features a large dedicated laundry room and two car garage.The Landings is a sought after neighborhood within 1 mile of Bay Haven Charter School, Nature Walk Golf Club and conveniently located close to grocery stores, local restaurants, shopping, and both Tyndall Air Force Base as well as the Navy Base. This home has it all and is a must see in person!
